{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Number 和 String 函數","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Functions_536f6bf46bbdf38cc1a0b28ca1bc41b9","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<h4 id=\"number_和_string_函數\">Number 和 String 函數</h4>\n<div class=\"onlyinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><code>Number</code> 和 <code>String</code> 函數讓你把物件轉換為數字或字串。這些函數的語句是︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var objRef=Number(objRef);\nvar objRef=String(objRef);\n</pre>\n<p>此處的 <code>objRef</code> 就是物件的參考。</p>\n<p>以下的範例把 <code><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_參考/全域物件/Date\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 參考/全域物件/Date\">Date</a></code> 物件轉換為可讀的字串。</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var D = new Date (430054663215);\n// 返回以下字串\n// \"Thu Aug 18 04:37:43 GMT-0700 (Pacific Daylight Time) 1983\"\nvar x = String(D);\n</pre>\n</div>\n\n<p>以下範例把 <code><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_參考/全域物件/String\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 參考/全域物件/String\">String</a></code> 物件轉換為 <a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_參考/全域物件/Number\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 參考/全域物件/Number\"><font face=\"Courier New\">Number</font></a> 物件。</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var str=\"12\";\nvar num=Number(str);\n</pre>\n<p>你可以使用 DOM 的方法 write() 和 JavaScript 的 typeof 運算子來檢驗。</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var str=\"12\";\ndocument.write(typeof str);\ndocument.write(\"&lt;br/&gt;\");\nvar num=Number(str);\ndocument.write(typeof num);\n</pre>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的函數/parseInt_和_parseFloat_函數\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/預先定義的函數/escape_和_unescape_函數\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Number 和 String 函數讓你把物件轉換為數字或字串。這些函數的語句是︰","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Functions","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/functions_536f6bf46bbdf38cc1a0b28ca1bc41b9","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/functions_536f6bf46bbdf38cc1a0b28ca1bc41b9/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Functions_536f6bf46bbdf38cc1a0b28ca1bc41b9","title":"Number 和 String 函數"}],"pageTitle":"Number 和 String 函數 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}